stateDiagram
    [*] --> Pending
    Pending --> Accepted
    Pending --> Rejected
    Accepted --> Preparing
    Preparing --> Ready
    Ready --> Completed
    
    Completed --> [*]
    Rejected --> [*]

    note right of Pending
        Customer places order.
        Waiting for Shop Owner.
    end note

    note left of Rejected
        Owner declines order.
        (e.g. Out of stock)
    end note

    note right of Accepted
        Owner accepts order.
        Kitchen starts prep.
    end note

    note right of Ready
        Food is packed.
        Waiting for pickup.
    end note
